  "detailed_description": "<strong><i>Coloring Game</i></strong> is a fantastic anti-stress game. Animate the pixel picture by coloring it in full!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Three playing modes.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Numbered pixels and highlighting the coloring area;<br></li><li>Numbered pixels only;<br></li><li>Highlighting the coloring area only.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The picture gets animated when the level is completed.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The game features a great array of additional tools which facilitate the coloring process: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Instant moving of the coloring area by clicking on the Navigator;<br></li><li>Selection of color by clicking the right mouse button;<br></li><li>Easy line coloring when holding the Shift button;<br></li><li>Opportunity to cancel any action by pressing the \u201cZ\u201d button.</li></ul>",
